Package: DTEAssurance
Type: Package
Title: Assurance Methods for Clinical Trials with a Delayed Treatment Effect
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("James", "Salsbury", email = "jsalsbury1@sheffield.ac.uk", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2584-3640"))
Description: Provides functions for planning clinical trials
    subject to a delayed treatment effect using assurance-based methods.
    Includes two Shiny applications that use these functions for
    interactive exploration, simulation, and visualization of trial designs
    and outcomes.
